<text top="2615" left="55" width="450" height="41" font="font0" id="p1_t1" reading_order_no="10" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">about  the  concept  of  ‘cleaner </text>
<text top="2654" left="55" width="447" height="41" font="font0" id="p1_t2" reading_order_no="11" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">living’.  This  will  enable  us  to </text>
<text top="2692" left="55" width="449" height="43" font="font1" id="p1_t3" reading_order_no="12" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">reach  the  other  88  per  cent  of </text>
<text top="2733" left="55" width="367" height="42" font="font2" id="p1_t4" reading_order_no="13" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">consumers  who  haven’t </text>
